           perform   pmt-cod-ime-000      thru pmt-cod-ime-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo provvigione per l'intermediario         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-pvf-ime-000      thru pmt-pvf-ime-999        .
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice forma di pagamento                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-fop-000      thru pmt-cod-fop-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Percentuale sconto pagamento                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-scp-aap-000      thru pmt-scp-aap-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice nostra banca di appoggio                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-nos-ban-000      thru pmt-nos-ban-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice ABI banca di appoggio per bonifici       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-abi-000      thru pmt-cod-abi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Codice CAB sportello banca di appoggio          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-cod-cab-000      thru pmt-cod-cab-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conto corrente bancario per bonifici            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-ccc-app-000      thru pmt-ccc-app-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Conto corrente postale                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-ccp-app-000      thru pmt-ccp-app-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Tipo addebito spese incasso                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spi-000      thru pmt-add-spi-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Si/No addebito spese bollo                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-add-spb-000      thru pmt-add-spb-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data scadenza manuale pagamento                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-pag-dsm-000      thru pmt-pag-dsm-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo quota a forfait su pagamento            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-pag-qaf-000      thru pmt-pag-qaf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo acconto su pagamento                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-pag-act-000      thru pmt-pag-act-999        .
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-999.
       pmt-tes-reg-999.
           exit.

