           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-cof-rif (1)    to   v-alf                  .
